      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's actually really unsettling. if it's being sent to a cloud server like you say, who exactly is on the other end of that? is it just the manufacturers? it feels like it's more than just \"improving my experience\" if they're tracking how i react to stress in my own kitchen. do you think there's a way to see if there's an active data stream being sent out specifically during these episodes?",
